.--------------------------------------------------------------------.
| File name | Description                                            |
|-----------|--------------------------------------------------------|
| rec       | Record screen (x11grab) and device audio (pulseaudio). |
|-----------|--------------------------------------------------------|
| rec-aud   | Record audio (pulse).                                  |
|-----------|--------------------------------------------------------|
| clr-test  | Test terminal color scheme.                            |
|-----------|--------------------------------------------------------|
| upl       | Upload file to arduino.                                |
'--------------------------------------------------------------------'
